       fit(type)
              Specify the fit type used to plot the data. Default
              straight line fit.

                   Fortran:
                        subroutine fit(type)
                        integer type

                   C:
                        fit(type)
                             int type;

                   Current fit types are:

                        0    -    No lines at all.
                        1    -    Straight line fit.
                        2    -    Cubic spline fit.
                        3    -    Least squares fit.
                        4    -    Power equation fit.
                        5    -    Saturated growth rate fit.


